## Limitations

The findings are based on available online resources and may not capture all recent developments in nursing technology. Additionally, the rapid pace of technological advancement means that some information may become outdated quickly. The analysis primarily focuses on the U.S. healthcare system, and the impact of technology on nursing may vary in different regions and healthcare settings.